        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Patrick]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p><code>--output SIZE,RO,TYPE</code> is a nice idea!</p>
<p>Yes, these are 0B loop devices but these are still read-write and not read-only. So as long we don’t really know their purpose, we don’t really know what we’re doing here. Just hiding a potential issue.</p>
<p>Thease are 0B at time of check as suggested by your pull request but there’s no guarantee that these stay 0B.</p>
<p>Asked just now:</p>
